<sect1 id="dir_1a83b528599da40ca3e2005a9bc9336b_1autotoc_md139">
<title>helios::engine::common</title><para>Shared type definitions, compile-time concepts, and role tags used across multiple engine subsystems.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1a83b528599da40ca3e2005a9bc9336b_1autotoc_md140">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides lightweight, system-agnostic infrastructure shared by all engine subsystems: interaction context structs, compile-time concepts for role classification, and tag types for the opt-in registration pattern.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_1a83b528599da40ca3e2005a9bc9336b_1autotoc_md141">
