</entry><entry thead="no"><para>C++20 concepts for engine role constraints (IsManagerLike, IsSystemLike, ...)  </para>
</entry></row>
<row>
<entry thead="no"><para><computeroutput>tags/</computeroutput>  </para>
</entry><entry thead="no"><para>Empty tag structs for compile-time role identification (ManagerRole, SystemRole)  </para>
</entry></row>
